# Loaded at runtime for general settings (and optional dev convenience). Real env always wins.
# Paths: OS config `molt-hub/.env`, then first `.env` walking up from cwd.
#
# GitHub / Jira OAuth **app** id + secret are not read at runtime. They are baked in when you
# `cargo build` / `cargo tauri build`: set the vars below in the environment or in a **repo** `.env`
# (see `crates/server/build.rs` — walks from `crates/server/` up to the repo root).
#
# GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=
# GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
# JIRA_CLIENT_SECRET=
# JIRA_CLIENT_ID=
# (MOLTHUB_* prefixed variants are also accepted by build.rs)
#
# MOLTHUB_JIRA_REDIRECT_URI=
# MOLTHUB_GITHUB_REDIRECT_URI=
# MOLTHUB_LOCAL_API_PORT=
# RUST_LOG=info
